  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tissa Vidarana says that the situation will worsen if people act contrary to their expectations - the President should understand",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "There is no good position among the people regarding the 22nd Amendment of the Constitution. No provision was incorporated in the 22nd Amendment to restrict or limit the powers of the President as an executive.",
        "President of the Lanka Sama Samaj Party Prof. Tissa Vidarana said that the President should understand that if he acts contrary to the expectations of the people, the current crisis will become more serious.",
        "When asked about the current political situation, he mentioned the above. The Podujana Peramuna-led government, including President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, should be held accountable for the economic crisis.",
        "Because of the two-thirds majority, the President was not consulted by the best parties. Bad decisions have put the whole country in crisis.",
        "The economic crisis has intensified into a political crisis. People rallied against the government and began to hate the entire political structure.",
        "The 20th Amendment to the Constitution was created at the behest of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and former Minister Bashil Rajapaksa.",
        "Bashil Rajapaksa, who has dual citizenship, acted in favor of the United States. The 20th amendment of the constitution should be completely repealed, the 19th amendment should be implemented with amendments, and the Rajapaksas, including President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, should completely withdraw from politics.",
        "People's struggle has been largely successful. The move to repeal the 20th Amendment of the Constitution has been taken and the Rajapaksas have also withdrawn from politics.",
        "Due to the fact that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa's resignation will cause a constitutional crisis, the issue is being considered in depth.",
        "There is not a good impression among the people regarding the 22nd amendment of the Constitution submitted by the Minister of Justice, President's Attorney Vijayadasa Rajapaksa.",
        "He said that the 22nd amendment draft has not been prepared for the expectation of the people. No provisions have been included in it to control and limit the power of the President."
      ],
